          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3640866/" class=" " title="Fiala.">Fiala.</a>
                (Stýská se mi po tobě.)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="19764605">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">3 A logical picture of facts is a thought.
3.1 In a proposition a thought finds an expression that can be perceived by the senses.
3.2 In a proposition a thought can be expressed in such a way that the elements of the propositional sign correspond to the objects of the thought.
3.201 I call such elements 'simple signs', and such a proposition 'completely analysed'.
3.25 A proposition has one a...</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-07-19 13:22</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>3 A logical picture of facts is a thought.
3.1 In a proposition a thought finds an expression that can be perceived by the senses.
3.2 In a proposition a thought can be expressed in such a way that the elements of the propositional sign correspond to the objects of the thought.
3.201 I call such elements 'simple signs', and such a proposition 'completely analysed'.
3.25 A proposition has one and only one complete analysis.
3.203 A name means an object. The object is its meaning.
2.22 In a proposition a name is a representative of an object.
2.26 A name cannot be dissected further by means of a definition: it is a primitive sign.</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







